text: The 1999-00 Austrian Cup is the cup competition in Austrian football. SK Sturm Graz were the defending champions. == Round 1 == First round with teams from the first and second league. ==Round of 32== The game was not played because St. Pölten was bankrupt ==Round of 16== ==Quarter-finals== ==Semi-finals== ==Final== ==Top goalscorers== Rank Player Club Goals 1 Igor Pamić Grazer AK 2 1 Anton Polster SV Austria Salzburg 2 Weltfußball.de ==References== Category:Austrian Cup Category:1999–2000 in European football
